  "title": "SSR fails due to call of window.encodeURI in numeric menu component",
  "body": "## 🐛 Bug description\r\n\r\nThe following call to window from https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/ccf159efcb94e9c8c04c558fcb69e2e3d8d79729/src/connectors/numeric-menu/connectNumericMenu.ts\r\n\r\n    const prepareItems = (state: SearchParameters) =>\r\n      items.map(({ start, end, label }) => ({\r\n        label,\r\n        value: (window as any).encodeURI(JSON.stringify({ start, end })),\r\n        isRefined: isRefined(state, attribute, { start, end, label }),\r\n      }));\r\n\r\n\r\ncauses SSR to fail when using the numeric menu\r\n\r\n## 🔍 Bug reproduction\r\n\r\n**Steps to reproduce the behavior:**\r\n\r\nThis live example is for vue-instantsearch which I am using, but I assume it happens for all flavors.\r\n\r\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/goofy-northcutt-kttko?file=/pages/search.vue\r\n\r\n## 💭 Expected behavior\r\n\r\nNo call to window\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\nI assume all\r\n\r\n",
